g.text: Understand business requirements, current needs, and future aspiratons.
Document needs and aspiratons to assess and analyze the environment for gaps
Leverage insttutonal knowledge and tools to formulate a plan
Strategize and prioritze based on capability, needs, and budgets
Provide leadership with a strategic plan with prioritzed tasks and milestones based on risk, impact, and costs.
Obtain acceptance, develop an executon plan, and present for approvals.
